Text: RE smubetas Fw For college football fansArtie very humorous although no mention was made of the teasippers from Austin Kevin Original Message From Art Kretz mailto Sent Friday September AM To SMU Betas Subject smubetas Fw For college football fans A bit of levity during these trying times my apologies to all you Big fans in Okieland kai bros Artie Original Message From WAYNE GARRAWAY To UndisclosedRecipientpimoutintprodigynet Sent Friday September AM Subject Fw For college football fans Original Message From To Cc Sent Friday August AM Subject Fwd For college football fans At Homecoming the BETA TENT had the biggest crowd by far Stay connected and consider a future homecoming BETA reunion Its incredibleforget the years in betweeneveryone just seems to pick it up right where they left off years ago Your use of Yahoo Groups is subject to infoterms Yahoo Groups Sponsor Get your FREE credit report with a FREE CreditCheck Monitoring Service trial MDsVHBbQCAAySSFAAVkqlBTM At Homecoming the BETA TENT had the biggest crowd by far Stay connected and consider a future homecoming BETA reunion Its incredibleforget the years in betweeneveryone just seems to pick it up right where they left off years ago Your use of Yahoo Groups is subject to infoterms

RE smubetas ers its time to hump itSpace Well said I remember some of these people begging for mercy in The Pit They were not as cocky then as they are now I was always proud of being one number lower than Strap Anderson indicating a marginally better GPA Original Message From hosman mailto Sent Monday October PM To Subject Re smubetas ers its time to hump it As a Beta from the distinguished class of and a Nebraskan living in Oklahoma I would like to make a few comments about the letters below from the distinguished Oklahoma weenie doctor Bill Miller and sharp tongued very popular Oklahoman transplanted author the one and only Jim Dent First NEBRASKA did not get stomped Second the great class of Picture attached who helped pledged you arrogant sissies from the classes of and think its time you get out the Loving Cup and pass it around again Finally neither Jim Dent or Bill Miller have invited any of the class of who reside in Oklahoma over for kai for Beek thats FF But we in the class of are not bitter even though a visit the beautiful and prestigious Nichols Hills Oklahomas answer to Highland Park would boost our spirits in these times Anyway I hope I speak for the silent EWooglincom members when I say Im glad I didnt buy any of that ENRON stock Oh and by the way no one need respond to this note as I remain affectionately yours Tom Hosman thats Space for Beek and for those of you who are still counting Original Message From Jim Dent To Sent Thursday October PM Subject Re smubetas ers its time to hump it Hey Bill Miller You stupid asshole Doug Dyer was not in our class I will admit that Mule Benson showed some guts in standing up for your wimp class You obviously dont have the guts You live two blocks from me and never even had the grace to say hello So stick it brother Wish I could take you back to the dorg Dent Original Message From To Sent Thursday October PM Subject Re smubetas ers its time to hump it Brother Benson Congratulations on taking over the top spot in the Bestofewooglincomcontest Those pathetic losers of have been shoving our faces in it for too long After all whose class was Doug Dyer in after all Sorry I cant come to D this we Got to go to parents weekend for my college freshman Dont forget to tune in to the Sooners stomping Nebraska kai B Miller At Homecoming the BETA TENT had the biggest crowd by far Stay connected and consider
